== 製作 ==
2020年3月，宣佈製作一部基於2015年電影《[[瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道|瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道]]》中的角色[[芙莉歐莎指揮官|芙莉歐莎]]的外傳電影，並有望由[[安雅·泰勒-喬伊|安雅·泰勒-喬伊]]主演，拍攝預計將於2021年開始進行<ref name="Furiosa">{{cite web||last1=Kroll|first=Justin|last2=Lang|first2=Brent|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/hollywood-productions-limbo-coronavirus-1203543478/|title=Hollywood’s Biggest Movies Are Stuck in Limbo as Start Dates Remain Uncertain|work=[[Variety|Variety]]|date=2020-03-26|accessdate=2020-10-13}}</ref>。2020年10月，確認由泰勒-喬伊出演芙莉歐莎，而[[克里斯·漢斯沃|克里斯·漢斯沃]]和[[葉海亞·阿巴杜-馬汀二世|葉海亞·阿巴杜-馬汀二世]]加盟演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|last=Kit|first=Borys|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/furiosa-anya-taylor-joy-chris-hemsworth-yahya-abdul-mateen-ii-to-star-in-mad-max-spinoff|title= 'Furiosa': Anya Taylor-Joy, Chris Hemsworth, Yahya Abdul-Mateen II to Star in 'Mad Max' Spinoff|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2020-10-13|accessdate=2020-10-13}}</ref>。多個《瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道》的工作團隊成員將回歸製作《芙莉歐莎》，包括剪輯師{{le|瑪格麗特·西賽爾|Margaret Sixel}}、藝術指導{{le|科林·吉布森|Colin Gibson (production designer)}}、混音師{{le|本·奥斯莫|Ben Osmo}}和化妝及髮型設計師{{le|萊絲莉·范德懷特|Lesley Vanderwalt}}<ref>{{cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2020/10/furiosa-mad-max-spinoff-george-miller-anya-taylor-joy-chris-hemsworth-1234596503/|title= ‘Mad Max’ Spinoff ‘Furiosa’ In The Works At Warners With George Miller Directing & Anya Taylor-Joy In Title Role; Chris Hemsworth & Yahya Abdul-Mateen II Along For Ride|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2020-10-13|accessdate=2020-10-13}}</ref>。2021年2月，曾為《瘋狂麥斯：憤怒道》配樂的[[Junkie_XL|Junkie XL]]確認回歸為《芙莉歐莎》進行配樂工作<ref>{{cite web|last=Zinski|first=Dan|url=https://screenrant.com/mad-max-furiosa-prequel-movie-junkie-xl-soundtrack/|title=Furiosa: Junkie XL Will Score the Mad Max Spinoff|work=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]]|date=2021-02-27|accessdate=2021-04-19}}</ref>。2021年4月，據[[新南威爾斯州長|新南威爾斯州長]][[格拉迪斯·貝爾吉格利安|格拉迪斯·貝爾吉格利安]]透露，該片收到了新南威爾斯州政府的1.75億澳元獎勵金和40%減稅，並將成為澳洲有史以來最大規模製作的電影，而且預估可以為澳洲帶來3.5億澳元的經濟收入和提供至少850個工作職缺<ref>{{cite web|last=Sharf|first=Zack|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2021/04/furiosa-biggest-film-ever-made-australia-1234631257/|title=‘Furiosa’ to Become the Biggest Film Ever Made in Australia, Plot Takes Place ‘Over Many Years’|work=[[IndieWire|IndieWire]]|date=2021-04-19|accessdate=2021-04-19}}</ref>。2021年11月，阿巴杜-馬汀二世因日程衝突退出，他的角色改由[[湯姆·伯克|湯姆·伯克]]接演<ref>{{cite web |last1=Kroll |first1=Justin |last2=D'Alessandro |first2=Anthony |title=Tom Burke Replaces Yahya Abdul-Mateen II In George Miller's 'Mad Max' Spinoff 'Furiosa' |url=https://deadline.com/2021/11/tom-burke-george-millers-mad-max-spin-off-furiosa-1234881181/ |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=2022-02-15 |date=2021-11-29}}</ref>。2022年1月，據報導{{le|西蒙·達根|Simon Duggan}}接替[[約翰·西爾|約翰·西爾]]擔任本片的攝影師<ref>{{cite web |last1=Dillard |first1=Samantha |title=ASC Welcomes New Member Simon Duggan |url=https://theasc.com/news/asc-welcomes-new-member-simon-duggan |website=[[American_Society_of_Cinematographers|American Society of Cinematographers]] |access-date=2022-02-15 |date=2022-01-19}}</ref>。

=== 拍攝 ===
[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]最初定於2022年3月在[[新南威爾斯州|新南威爾斯州]]開始進行<ref>{{cite web|last=Lutz|first=John|title='Furiosa': Anya Taylor-Joy Is Learning to Stunt Drive for 'Mad Max: Fury Road' Prequel|url=https://collider.com/anya-taylor-joy-furiosa-prequel-stunts/|publisher=[[Collider|Collider]] |date=2021-08-26|access-date=2021-08-30}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Fuge |first1=Jonathan |title=Mad Max: Furiosa Set to Begin Filming in March |url=https://movieweb.com/mad-max-furiosa-begin-filming-march/ |website=[[MovieWeb|MovieWeb]] |access-date=2022-02-15 |date=2022-01-20}}</ref>。製作於2022年5月開始進行<ref>{{cite web |last1=Utichi |first1=Joe |title=Inside George Miller’s 20-Year Quest To Make ''Three Thousand Years Of Longing'', As ''Furiosa'' Revs Her Engines – Cannes |url=https://deadline.com/2022/05/george-miller-cannes-three-thousand-years-of-longing-1235020237/ |website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=2022-05-17 |date=2022-05-17}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
《芙莉歐莎》由[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟]]原定於2023年6月23日上映<ref>{{cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2020/12/warner-bros-dates-three-pics-for-2023-theatrical-release-not-hbo-max-furiosa-coyote-vs-acme-the-color-purple-1234661184/|title=Warner Bros. Dates Three Pics For 2023 Theatrical Release (Not HBO Max): ‘Furiosa’, ‘Coyote Vs. Acme’ & ‘The Color Purple’|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2020-12-23|accessdate=2020-12-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Rubin|first=Rebecca|url=https://variety.com/2020/film/news/warner-bros-mad-max-fury-road-color-purple-1234874609/|title=Warner Bros. to Release ‘Mad Max: Fury Road’ Prequel and ‘The Color Purple’ Musical in Theaters in 2023|work=[[Variety|Variety]]|date=2020-12-23|accessdate=2020-12-24}}</ref>。2021年9月，宣佈電影延期至2024年5月24日上映<ref>{{cite web|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|url=https://deadline.com/2021/09/warner-bros-moves-furiosa-to-memorial-day-weekend-2024-salems-lot-to-fall-2022-1234830681/|title=Warner Bros. Moves ‘Mad Max’ Spinoff ‘Furiosa’ To Memorial Day Weekend 2024; ‘Salem’s Lot’ To Debut Early Fall 2022|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2021-09-10|accessdate=2021-09-10}}</ref>。

